high_descs: Turn right, walk to the sofa chair, turn right and walk to the middle of the long sofa.
Pick up the pillow from the sofa.
Turn left and walk to the chair with the red credit card on it.
Place the pillow on the left side of the chair.
Turn around and walk to the end of the sofa where the other pillow is at.
Pick up the pillow from the sofa.
Turn left and walk to the chair with the red credit card on it.
Place the pillow on the right side of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place the two pillows from the long sofa on to the chair with the red credit card.

high_descs: Turn right towards the chair, then turn left towards the couch underneath the window.
Pick up the pillow in the middle of the couch.
Turn around then turn right and walk towards the chair.
Place the pillow on the left side inside the chair on top of the credit card.
Turn around then walk towards the black cabinet, then turn towards the couch.
Pick up the pillow on the right side of the couch.
Turn around then turn right and walk towards the chair.
Place the pillow in the chair on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Place two pillows inside the chair, one on the left and one on the right.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sofa containing the two pillows.
Pick up the pillow on the left.
Turn left and walk to the chair containing the red credit card.
Put the pillow on top of the credit card and leaning against the left arm rest.
Turn around and walk to the other pillow on the sofa.
Pick up the other pillow from the sofa.
Turn left and walk back to the same chair.
Put the other pillow on the chair, leaning against the right arm rest.
anns.task_desc: Move two pillows from a sofa to a chair.
